OL,3,CMan jailed for #51,000 Rolex theft in
OL,4,CKendal
OL,6,FA man who stole more than #50,000
OL,7,Fworth of Rolex watches from a Kendal
OL,8,Fjeweller has been given an 18-month
OL,9,Fprison sentence.
OL,11,FThe father of three from Rochdale
OL,12,Fadmitted theft.
OL,14,FCarlisle Crown Court heard today that
OL,15,FBagasan Graham, 32, also known as
OL,16,FJohari Nasir Carter had a lengthy list
OL,17,Fof similar crimes under 17 different
OL,18,Fnames and has spent seven years of his
OL,19,Fadult life behind bars
