OL,3,CMan jailed for #51,000 Rolex theft in
OL,4,CKendal
OL,6,FOn 14th June, 2022, Graham and a
OL,7,Ffemale accomplice went to a tyre
OL,8,Fcentre in Kendal where staff
OL,9,Funknowingly fitted false number plates
OL,10,Fto a Nissan Micra.
OL,12,FHis partner-in-crime entered the Banks
OL,13,FLyon store in Kendal where she showed
OL,14,Fan interest in a number of expensive
OL,15,Fwatches.
OL,17,FShe left the store initially before
OL,18,Fmaking a return visit, asking the
OL,19,Fowner to see four Rolex watches.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
