OL,4,CKendal
OL,6,F"Staff were comfortable, offering her
OL,7,Fa coffee while she made her decision
OL,8,Fabout what they thought was going to
OL,9,Fbe an expensive purchase," said
OL,10,Fprosecutor Brendan Burke.
OL,12,F"While the owner was distracted,
OL,13,Flooking out of the front window of the
OL,14,Fshop, the accomplice grabbed all four
OL,15,Fwatches with a collective value of
OL,16,F#51,600 and fled the shop."
