OL,6,FShe was seen by a bystander running
OL,7,Fdown the street before getting into
OL,8,Fthe Micra driven by Graham, who the
OL,9,Fprosecutor said was the crime's "chief
OL,10,Fprotagonist".
OL,12,FThe duo drove to Oxenholme railway
OL,13,Fstation where Graham caught a train
OL,14,Fsouth but he was later detained and
OL,15,Fidentified from CCTV footage.
OL,17,FHis accomplice was later stopped on
OL,18,Fthe M6 but no watches were found or
OL,19,Frecovered.
