OL,4,CKendal
OL,6,FA defence barrister told the court
OL,7,Fthat a gambling addiction lay behind
OL,8,FGraham's offending following a
OL,9,Ftraumatic and challenging early life.
OL,11,FHe said the father-of-three had since
OL,12,Ftaken steps to rehabilitate himself,
OL,13,Fwas seeking to take a maths degree,
OL,14,Fopen a barber shop and set a good
OL,15,Fexample to his young sons.
OL,17,FJudge Nicholas Barker had said of his
OL,18,Foffending: "It is not shop theft. It
OL,19,Fis a sophisticated form of thieving."
